From,their,site,SwapThing,is,a,community,of,users,who,want,to,swap,buy,and,sell,things,in,a,new,way,The,purpose,of,the,SwapThing,Open,API,is,to,share,data,and,increase,the,opportunities,to,swap,Our,API,is,built,in,simple,HTTP,XML,so,everyone,can,use,it,The,API,provides,two,basic,sets,of,functionality,Tag,Searches,Give,us,a,tag,and,we,ll,give,you,a,feed,of,item,data,Choose,how,you,want,to,use,and,format,it,Item,Details,If,you,are,not,using,all,the,data,from,the,feed,and,have,a,request,for,more,info,on,a,specific,item,you,can,send,us,the,Item,ID,from,the,original,feed,and,we,will,return,the,data,on,that,item